{
  "texts": [
    "Equally, a quality Foreword vii inspection system might involve machine learning, multiple IoT sensing devices and digital twin model of the item being inspected.Further, we note that many Industries 4.0 technologies (including AI) are often heavily dependent on internet connectivity and cloud computing resources.",
    "Also, most AI methods fall short of providing a firm guarantee of the results they provide.",
    "These pose two additional, self-explanatory challenges.Challenge 3: Data security and privacy remain significant causes of concern for industrial companies when considering new technologies (including AI).",
    "Challenge 4:The lack of performance guarantees is a significant cause of concern for industrial companies when considering many AI-derived approaches.These four challenges collectively have inhibited the industrial take up of AI until recent times.",
    "An inaccessible technology, hard to match to industrial needs and with concerns about data and its lack of performance guarantees."
  ]
}